OL,3,CJersey government staff costs go up by
OL,4,C#73 million
OL,6,FThere are questions about the number
OL,7,Fof public servants in and the amount
OL,8,Fthey are paid after the latest States
OL,9,Fof Jersey financial accounts were
OL,10,Fpublished.
OL,12,FIn 2023, staff costs hit #73 million -
OL,13,Fa 14% increase from the previous year.
OL,15,FChief Minister Lyndon Farnham says
OL,16,Fthings need to change and has
OL,17,Fsuggested that there could be job cuts
OL,18,Fin the future.
