OL,3,CJersey government staff costs go up by
OL,4,C#73 million
OL,6,FIt is an issue constantly debated in
OL,7,FJersey and the new accounts published
OL,8,Flast week give a clear picture of just
OL,9,Fhow much is spent on public servants
OL,10,Fsuch as teachers, medics and States
OL,11,FMembers.
OL,13,FThe accounts show that #593 million
OL,14,Fwas spent on staff in 2023, an
OL,15,Fincrease from the year before due to a
OL,16,Fpay rise and extra employees.
OL,18,FWe have also confirmed that there will
OL,19,Fbe an 8% pay rise for all public
OL,20,Fservants this year, which will cost
OL,21,Faround #51 million.
