OL,3,CJersey government staff costs go up by
OL,4,C#73 million
OL,6,F"I suspect there may be some back
OL,7,Foffice jobs where we will look to see
OL,8,Fif we need perhaps more replacement. I
OL,9,Fimagine we would do it more by not
OL,10,Freplacing vacancies."
OL,12,FOf highest earners, six people's total
OL,13,Fpay after pension and benefits was
OL,14,Fmore than #200,000.
OL,16,FThe top earner in 2023 cost more than
OL,17,F#245,000.
OL,19,FIn comparison, State Members
OL,20,Fthemselves are paid around #50,000.
