OL,6,FThat is largely because the Government
OL,7,Fhas to pay premium prices for skilled
OL,8,Fpeople who otherwise would be
OL,9,Fattracted to the private sector.
OL,11,FHowever, it raises difficult questions
OL,12,Ffor a Council of Ministers trying to
OL,13,Fslim down expenditure.
